data.description: This recently spruced up home in the charming borough of Forest Hills boasts newly refinished hardwood flooring and fresh paint throughout, great curb appeal, and a modern kitchen and bathroom.  The lower level, which includes its own full bathroom, has a bonus room that can be utilized as a 4th bedroom, exercise room, or office. There is plenty of potential to sculpt the over-sized backyard into an outdoor sanctuary.  Move right in and call it home.
